1. Compile scss into css:
    npm run css:scss

2. Install package as dev dependency
    npm -i -D <package name>

3. Add autoprefixes to css
    npm run css:autoprefixer  

4. Run linter
    npm run css:lint

5. Run both scss compile and autoprefixer & linter
    npm run build:css


Commands 1,3,4,5 can all be found in package-lock.json

https://wweb.dev/blog/how-to-create-static-website-npm-scripts/